}

' Flow relationships
MiniAppFile --> JSApiFile : 1. dsbridge.call()
JSApiFile --> FactoryFile : 2. getEventDispatcher('dc')
FactoryFile --> DCDispatcherFile : 3. Returns DCJsEventDispatcher
DCDispatcherFile --> DCUseCaseFile : 4. createAppDataChannel()
DCUseCaseFile --> MiniAppMgrFile : 5. createDC()
MiniAppMgrFile --> DCMgrFile : 6. createApplicationDataChannels()
DCMgrFile --> DCServiceMgrFile : 7. createImsDc()
DCServiceMgrFile --> ServiceControllerFile : 8. AIDL Call
ServiceControllerFile --> ModemImpl : 9. Create DC
ModemImpl --> IIDCCallbackFile : 10. Callback
IIDCCallbackFile --> DCMgrFile : 11. onApplicationDataChannelResponse()
DCMgrFile --> MiniAppMgrFile : 12. onDataChannelCreated()
MiniAppMgrFile --> MiniAppFile : 13. Notify mini app

InCallServiceFile .down.> MiniAppMgrFile : Initializes
InCallServiceFile .down.> DCMgrFile : Initializes
IIDCFile .up.> ModemImpl : Implemented by

note bottom of ModemImpl
  **Terminal Implementation**
  Provided by phone manufacturer (Qualcomm, MediaTek, etc.)
  Must implement 3GPP TS.71 specification
  Handles actual 5G radio communication
end note

legend right
  |= Layer |= Purpose |
  | Mini App | User interface (HTML5/JS) |
  | Bridge | JS ↔ Native translation |
  | Dispatcher | Event routing |
  | Use Case | Business logic & validation |
  | Manager | State management & orchestration |
  | Service | Lifecycle & AIDL wrapper |
  | AIDL | Interface to terminal |
  | Terminal | Modem/chipset implementation |
endlegend

